{"lemma":"خِلْفَة","slug":"خِلْفَة","root":"خ.ل.ف","root_slug":"خ-ل-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خِلْفَة","root":"خلف","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11342","n11354","n11355","n11356"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%90%D9%84%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11342","headword_ar":"خلّفهُ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xl~fhu waraA='ahu","text_ar":"خلّفهُ وَرَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxoliyfN","text_ar":"تَخْلِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He left him behind him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) namely, a man: (S, Msb, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafahu","text_ar":"خَلَفَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[signifies the same: or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made him to be behind him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlfhu","text_ar":"اخلفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q.v.], and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axtlfhu","text_ar":"اختلفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [whence the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloHaHotu EalaY fulaAnK","text_ar":"اَلْحَحْتُ عَلَى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlAitibaAEi Hat~aY A@xotalafotuhu","text_ar":"فِى الاِتِبَاعِ حَتَّى ا@خْتَلَفْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I pressed upon such a one in following"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until I made him to be behind me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xal~afahumo","text_ar":"خَلَّفَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went, before them; and left them behind him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xl~fwA A^avoqAlahum","text_ar":"خلّفوا اَثْقالَهُم"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They left their loads,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baggage &c., behind their backs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) when they went away to draw water. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xl~fhu","text_ar":"خلّفهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appointed him, his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyfap","text_ar":"خَلِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"successor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vice-agent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; (K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astxlfhu","text_ar":"استخلفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) So in the Kur [xxiv. 54], ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layasotaxilafan~ahumo","text_ar":"لَيَسْتَخِلَفَنَّهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY A@loA^aroDi kamaA A@sotaxolafa A@l~a*iyna mino qabolihimo","text_ar":"فِى ا@لْاَرْضِ كَمَا ا@سْتَخْلَفَ ا@لَّذِينَ مِنْ قَبْلِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That He will assuredly make them to be successors in the earth, like as He made to be successors those who were before them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xl~f binaAqatihi","text_ar":"خلّف بِنَاقَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n. as above, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bound one of the teats of his she-camel with the thing termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiraAr","text_ar":"صِرَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in order that her young one might not suck it]: (S, K:) from Yaakoob. (S.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":794}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n11354","headword_ar":"خَلْفَةٌ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11355","headword_ar":"خُلْفَةٌ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulofN","text_ar":"خُلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vice, a fault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an imperfection:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"badness, corruptness, vitiousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dishonesty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foolishness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stupidity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"paucity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"want, of intellect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understanding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaAfapN","text_ar":"خَلَافَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly an inf. n., of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalufa","text_ar":"خَلُفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and before mentioned as such; (see 1, in the latter half of the paragraph;)] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"idiocy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) All of these meanings have been assigned to it in explanations of the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abiyEuka h`*aA AlEaboda","text_ar":"اَبِيعُكَ هٰذَا العَبْدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^aboraA^u A_ilayoka mino xulofatihi","text_ar":"وَاَبْرَاُ اـِلَيْكَ مِنْ خُلْفَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sell to thee this slave, but I am irresponsible to thee for his vice, &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, accord. to IAar, the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAfihi","text_ar":"خِلَافِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his contrariousness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last taste"},{"kind":"text","text":"of food; (K;) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu laTay~ibu Alxulofapi","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَطَيِّبُ الخُلْفَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily it is good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet, in respect of the last taste"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofapN","text_ar":"خَلْفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulafN","text_ar":"خُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and it ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulofapN","text_ar":"خُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loss of appetite for food, in consequence of disease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so accord. to the CK:) [or,] accord. to some copies of the K, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofapN","text_ar":"خَلْفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has this latter signification; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulafN","text_ar":"خُلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": accord. to other copies,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulafN","text_ar":"خُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofapN","text_ar":"خَلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sense: but both these readings require consideration: what is found in the Lexicons is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafato nafosuhu","text_ar":"خَلَفَتْ نَفْسُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani AlT~aEaAmi","text_ar":"عَنِ الطَّعَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; meaning as explained above, in the latter half of the first paragraph. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n11356","headword_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of coming after"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiEodapN","text_ar":"قِعْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ a mode, or manner, of sitting. ” (Msb.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulofN","text_ar":"خُلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  It signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Difference"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of any kind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, * TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming and going"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the night and the day; (S, K, * TA;) and likewise of wild animals. (K.) Hence the saying in the Kur [xxv. 63],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wahuwa A@l~a*iY jaEala A@ll~ayola waA@ln~ahaAra","text_ar":"وَهُوَ ا@لَّذِى جَعَلَ ا@للَّيْلَ وَا@لنَّهَارَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapF","text_ar":"خِلْفَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, *) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaY xilofapK","text_ar":"ذَوَى خِلْفَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Bd,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And He it is who hath made the night and the day"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that each replaces the other:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each follows the other:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that he who is unable to accomplish a thing in the night may do it in the day, and the reverse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, L, K.) Zuheyr says, of wild animals,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yamo$iyna xilofapF","text_ar":"يَمْشِينَ خِلْفَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They go to and fro."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA. [See Em p. 109.]) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*atohu xilofapN","text_ar":"اَخَذَتْهُ خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was"},{"kind":"page_break","n":797},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taken with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affection causing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a frequent going to and from the privy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A discharging of the bowels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a purging and vomiting together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disordered state of the stomach arising from"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unwholesome"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"food;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a looseness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diarrhœa."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofN","text_ar":"خِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bringing"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the watering-place in the evening, after the people have gone away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) ―         -b6-  And A man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"watching to see another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano yunaAZira","text_ar":"اَنْ يُنَاظِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in some copies of the K, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"An yunaASira","text_ar":"ان يُنَاصِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in other copies, being put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"An yubaASiru","text_ar":"ان يُبَاصِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the right reading, agreeably with an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aixotalafa","text_ar":"اِخْتَلَفَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAHibahu","text_ar":"صَاحِبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [for which see 3, near the middle of the paragraph,] TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and when he is absent from his family, going in to them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or [rather],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he is absent from his wife, going in to her."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, after the explanation of the phrase above mentioned.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is suspended behind the rider;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is suspended behind the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of vehicle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHomil","text_ar":"مَحْمِل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Remains"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water in a trough or tank. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What remains, of food, between the teeth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage, that comes forth after another plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which has become dry, and broken in pieces:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that comes forth not from rain, but by reason of the cold of the latter part of the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Ziyád El-Kilábee, K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabolN","text_ar":"رَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What the trees disclose in the beginning of the cold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safariy~ap","text_ar":"صَفَرِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit that comes forth after other fruit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit that comes forth after abundant fruit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, TA;) this being termed the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofap","text_ar":"خِلْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of trees: (S, Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a growth of leaves after the falling away of other leaves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwna","text_ar":"دُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the K is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoda","text_ar":"بَعْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaves that come forth after the first leaves, in the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"season called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Nh, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What grows in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"summer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; so says A 'Obeyd: (S, K:) or, (JK, Mgh, K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofN","text_ar":"خِلْفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage produced by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Syf","text_ar":"صيف"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Syf","text_ar":"صيف"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the springherbage has dried up."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Mgh.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A produce of grape-vines after the grapes have turned black; the grapes being gathered while it is fresh and green, it then ripens:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so other fruits:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a new produce, by the vine, of fresh sour grapes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grain that is sown"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, * Mgh, K *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the former has come to maturity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:) because taken as a substitute for wheat and barley: (K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilafN","text_ar":"خِلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece with which a garment is patched"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it is old and worn out."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A time after a time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Differing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one from another"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"others"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofN","text_ar":"خِلْفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) it is applied in this sense to a people, or company of men: (AZ, S, K:) and to beasts, or horses or the like, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"differing"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in their colours and appearances:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofataAni","text_ar":"خِلْفَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to any two things that are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"different;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofaAni","text_ar":"خِلْفَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ks, Msb, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofataAni","text_ar":"خِلْفَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, TA,) to any two colours that are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"combined"},{"kind":"text","text":"[because"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"different"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ks, K, TA.) AZ cites, as an ex., the saying [of a rájiz],"},{"kind":"quote","text":"saAqiyaAhumaA ↓ \n      dalowaAYo xilofaAni"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My two buckets are different, and their two suppliers with water"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, TA;) meaning that one of them [i. e. of the buckets] is ascending and full, and the other is descending and empty; or that one of them is new, and the other is old and worn out. (TA, in two places.) And one says of two children, or two male slaves; or two female slaves, that they are"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofataAni","text_ar":"خِلْفَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofaAni","text_ar":"خِلْفَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) applying to the male and the female, (TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One tall and the other short:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one white and the other black."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, K.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banuw fulaAnK","text_ar":"بَنُو فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The children of such a one are half males and half females."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nitaAju fulaAnK","text_ar":"نِتَاجُ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The offspring of the beasts of such a one are one year male and another year female."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waladato xilofayoni","text_ar":"وَلَدَتْ خِلْفَيْنِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of ewe or goat, (K,) or of a camel, (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She brought forth one year a male and another year a female."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) The pl. [of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofN","text_ar":"خِلْفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (K, TA) in all its senses (TA) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolaAfN","text_ar":"اَخْلَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilafapN","text_ar":"خِلَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, * TA;) the latter, [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiradapN","text_ar":"قِرَدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirodN","text_ar":"قِرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Bd","K","TA","S","Msb","Mgh","JK","AZ","Ks","L"]}]}}